Life expectancy data in 1998

Source: R/data-lifeexp.R
lifeexp.Rd

Imported from the example dataset lifeexp.dta in Stata. This dataset contains variable labels and value labels.

Usage

lifeexp

Format

A tibble with 68 rows and 6 variables:

region

Region (with value labels)

country

Country

popgrowth

Average annual population growth rate (%)

lexp

Life expectancy at birth (years)

gnppc

GNP per capita

safewater

Safe water (%)

Examples

lifeexp
#> # A tibble: 68 × 6
